# Task Management App

## Setup

### 1. Run with Docker
docker-compose up --build

### 2. backend
http://localhost:7000

### 3. forntend
http://localhost:3000

## Features
- JWT Authentication
- CRUD Task Management
- Role-based access (Admin/User)
- MySQL Database

## Test
Use Postman or browser

or

### 1. run local
- cd backend
- py app.py
- http://localhost:7000/swagger

- cd frontend
- npm install
- npm start
- http://localhost:3000/register
- http://localhost:3000/login

### remark
database -> using my local postgresql
swagger -> not fully function
test using -> dashboard good, postman good
